text: The Reserve wines are unique blend created from selections by Albert Allahham and Alessandro Giardiello during their journey to Israel at the beginning of
2020. After tasting multiple premium barrels from a single vineyard, The Reserve blends were born. The result is a balanced, medium to full bodied blend of
Cabernet Sauvignon & Merlot with beautiful notes of mature black fruits, berries, a hint of pepper and delicate tannins, meanwhile the Chardonnay is a medium
to full body wine with tropical aromas and a long-lasting �nish.
